name.ja: <ruby>虹眼の星猫<rt>レインボーアイズ・スターキャット</rt></ruby>

requirement.en: You have another face-up monster with 200 DEF on your field during the turn you Normal Summoned this card.

effect.en: Send cards from the top of your Deck to the Graveyard equal to [the number of face-up Level 7 or higher monsters on the field]. Then, if a monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can add up to 2 Level 7 monsters with 200 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.
